* model selection

  * metafeatures
  * model/data complexity matching
  * sufficiency assessment

* model training

  * training-data partitioning
  * training-data augmentation
  * leakage, bias and label errors

* model evaluation

  * performance
  * calibration
  * fairness and generalization
  * robustness and fault tolerance

