* data shifts

  * covariate shift - data monitoring
  * label shift - prediction monitoring
  * concept drift

* data monitoring

  * data distribution-shift

* feature monitoring

  * feature distribution-shift

* model monitoring

  * prediction distribution-shift
  * uncertainty/confidence shifts
  * accuracy/performance metrics

